IT is reported, That one of them, under
• tanding that his Dead Body was to be kept and Hung in Iron in a Gibbet, Said upon it;
Now a Righteous GOD is going to fulfil that Word; THE EYE WHICH DESPISES TO OBEY A MOTHER, THE RAVENS OF THE VALLEY SHALL PICK IT OUT, AND THE YOUNG EAGLES SHALL EAT IT.
